diff --git a/libavfilter/split.c b/libavfilter/split.c
--- a/libavfilter/split.c
+++ b/libavfilter/split.c
Description: Allow asplit audio filter to accept ALL channel formats
and channel counts without format negotiation restrictions.

Without this patch, splitting multi-channel audio (e.g., 8ch 5.1+stereo)
can fail during filter graph negotiation because asplit doesn't declare
explicit format support.

This forces asplit to pass through any format, matching the behavior
needed for professional multi-channel broadcast workflows.

